#: data/campaigns/The_Rise_Of_Wesnoth/scenarios/02_The_Fall.cfg:140
#: data/campaigns/The_Rise_Of_Wesnoth/scenarios/02_The_Fall.cfg:141
#: data/campaigns/The_Rise_Of_Wesnoth/scenarios/02_The_Fall.cfg:142
